Requirements:

Requirements can be classed in 2 ways: 

Functional Requirements:
User Management: The system shall allow users to register, login, and manage profiles.
Booking Engine: The system shall allow students to select a date/time and confirm an
appointment with a specific doctor.
Conflict Validation: The system shall prevent two students from booking the same time slot for
the same doctor.
Administrative Control: The system shall allow Admins to add/remove doctors and edit the
global clinic schedule.

Non-Functional Requirements:
Usability: The UI must be intuitive enough for a first-time user to book an appointment in under
2 minutes.
Availability: The system should be accessible 24/7 for students to book appointments outside
of clinic operating hours.
Security: All user data and appointment history must be protected via secure login and session
management.
